document_data.Notable Rods of Absorption:
* The [[Lion Sword]] was assumed to work as one such rod per some sources.{{cite book/Villain's Lorebook|114}}
* [[Asmodeus]] was said, in some early sources, to have such a rod.{{cite book/Monster Manual 1st edition|21}}
* King [[Lhaeo]] possessed a unique version of this rod, the ''[[Monarch's Rod]]''.{{cite book/Lands of Intrigue/Erlkazar and Folk of Intrigue|27}}
* [[Imvaernarhro]]'s ''necklace of absorption'' functioned as such a rod did.{{cite book/Power of Faerûn|121}}
